{"title":"渴望","authors":["陈万鹏"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":5,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京电视机厂  陈万鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你的骨灰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着虹彩，撒入大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那波峰浪谷间——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有一束白花盛开！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我多想扑进大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为一滴海水，把它抚爱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，还是变成只海蚌吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张开蚌壳，把一星骨灰接住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸着我生命的浆液磨砺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为世间，捧出珍珠！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}